{"id":856464,"date":[{"year":1992,"month":1,"day":14}],"page":"6","source":"","region":"","masthead":"文艺百家","special_issue":"文艺百家","column":"","genre":"","count":"129","ytitle":"","mtitle":"《新世说》","ftitle":"","authors":["公输鲁"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入9号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1992\\01\\921e060801.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>梁实秋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梁实秋晚年哀叹:“懂得了世故就失去了天真。逝者如斯，无可奈何。”</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入9号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1992\\01\\921e060802.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>台双垣</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>冯亦代"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七十年代中期，冯亦代在湖北沙洋劳动。某日，想去镇上吃鱼，同行伙伴命冯装成北京来的“首长”模样，以假乱真，竟然偿愿，大快朵颐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公输鲁　撰文　台双垣　作画</FONT>"}]}